sequenceDiagram
    actor Patient as Paciente
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant TRIAGE as Triage Module
    participant CASES as Professional Cases
    participant PROF as Frontend Profesional

    Patient->>API: Solicita resultado de consulta
    API->>TRIAGE: Evaluar umbral de riesgo
    TRIAGE->>CASES: Crear caso escalado
    TRIAGE-->>API: Estado escalated
    API-->>Patient: Informar remision a profesional
    PROF->>API: GET /professional/cases
    API->>CASES: Obtener casos pendientes
    CASES-->>API: Lista de casos escalados
    API-->>PROF: Casos con evidencia y recomendacion
